---
const tidyCalUrl = 'https://tidycal.com/jessie-parkinson/intro-call';
---
<section class="book-section" id="book">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="book-grid">
      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="section-label">Let's talk</div>
        <h2 class="display">Book a 15-minute <em>intro call.</em></h2>
        <p>No pitch, no pressure. We'll talk about where you are, what you're trying to build, and whether this is the right fit. If it isn't, you'll still walk away with something useful.</p>

        <div class="book-meta">
          <div class="book-meta-item">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" /><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14" /></svg>
            15 minutes, short, direct, useful.
          </div>
          <div class="book-meta-item">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z" /></svg>
            Get a clear read on whether we're a fit.
          </div>
          <div class="book-meta-item">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" /></svg>
            Walk away with one actionable insight, fit or not.
          </div>
        </div>

        <a href={tidyCalUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary">
          <span>Find a time that works</span>
          <svg class="arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7" /></svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="tidycal-slot reveal" data-delay="2">
        <div class="tidycal-embed" data-path="jessie-parkinson/intro-call"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script src="https://asset-tidycal.b-cdn.net/js/embed.js" async is:inline></script>
